<%#
  Partial : _wrapper.html.erb
  Date    : 11/12/2025
  Author  : Moisés Reis
  Package : Meta

  Description:
    Outermost grid wrapper for all authentication views.
    Establishes a six-column layout that partitions the screen between
    the decorative background panel and the centered form container.

  ============================================================
  Notes
  ============================================================

  - This partial accepts no locals and applies no conditional logic.
  - Column spans for child sections (background, container) are defined
    by the partials yielded into it, not here.

  @yield  [content]  The background and container partials rendered inside the grid.
%>

<section class="relative grid grid-cols-6">
  <%= yield %>
</section>